State.Author: Hitme

State.Name: (AT) Hitme's Spouse Portraits Reworked

State.Description: My version of the wizard's ex wife. Full NPC with events, dialogue and out-of-hut schedule!
State.Name: Alecto the Witch (new NPC)

State.Author: ruanimal

State.Author: UncleArya
State.Description: Adds an additional minecart location for the beach using Content Patcher.
State.Name: Beach Minecart (CP)

State.Author: NCarigon
State.Description: Flavored honey now produces flavored meads. Also converts honey and mead into colored items, based on the honey flavor.
State.Name: Better Honey Mead

State.Author: Ben and ParadigmNomad
State.Description: Adds about 2600 new lines of dialogue across all 34 characters who have a heart level.
State.Name: Canon-Friendly Dialogue Expansion

State.Name: Clear Glasses - HD Graphics Depixelation and Filters

State.Author: Cornucopia
State.Description: Adds more crops, bushes, and trees to the game. Fully configurable and written to rely primarily on Content Patcher.
State.Name: Cornucopia - More Crops

State.Author: PeacefulEnd
State.Description: Framework for creating custom entities that can be spawned on maps or follow you around in Stardew Valley.
State.Name: Custom Companions

State.Author: atravita
State.Description: Makes Demetrius visit his little experiment in the farm cave sometimes. Also gives him 80+ lines of dialogue to use, consisting mostly of science facts, dad jokes, and the occasional rant about Reviewer 2.
State.Name: Demetrius Visits Farm Cave Redux

State.Author: Airyn and the DSV Team
State.Description: Adds ethnic, cultural, body type, ability, and gender diversity to Pelican Town, with complete seasonal outfits for all villagers! Seasonal outfits can be used for both vanilla designs & alternate designs.
State.Name: Diverse Stardew Valley - Seasonal Outfits (DSV)

State.Author: LemurKat and Kdau
State.Description:
Welcome to East Scarp! 

An expansion adding new NPCs; new locations; new fish; shops; special orders - and secrets.

In a picturesque location by the sea.
State.Name: East Scarp

State.Author: TheMightyAmondee
State.Description: Limit the amount of events seen in a day or in a row to increase story immersion.
State.Name: Event Limiter

State.Author: Novaphene
State.Description: Alternative Texture conversion for DustBeauty's industrial furniture
State.Name: (AT) DustBeauty's Industrial Furniture

State.Author: Airyn
State.Description: No more disappearing beach bridge at the luau!
State.Name: Fixed Luau Bridge

State.Author: desto
State.Description: Inhabitants will like items less each time you gift them that same item. Stop littering them with low-effort gifts!
State.Name: Gift Decline

State.Author: Cherry
State.Description: Make Hay Bales placed around your farm work as functional Silos
State.Name: Hay Bales as Silos

State.Author: Himetarts and Wildflour
State.Description: .Whimsical fountains for DGA.
State.Name: (DGA) HxW Fairy Fountain Furniture

State.Author: Himetarts and Wildflour
State.Description: Stylish and practical greenhouse furniture set for DGA or AT.
State.Name: (DGA AT) HxW Greenhouse Furniture

State.Author: mistyspring
State.Description: Custom resources, custom mixed seeds, eating animations, and more. 1.6 framework
State.Name: Item Extensions Framework

State.Author: Lumisteria
State.Description: This mod adds a new area to visit, with everything you could expect : events, npcs, items, secrets, recipes, flowers, and more.
State.Name: Lumisteria Visit Mt Vapius

State.Author: DecidedlyHuman
State.Description: This mod does nothing on its own. Its primary purpose is to allow map authors to spice up their maps with the new custom tile properties, extra features, etc., that this mod adds.
State.Name: Mapping Extensions and Extra Properties (MEEP)

State.Author: LemurKat
State.Description:
Jas is a lonely child, with only Vincent to play with, and the two adults in her life having little time with her, so what she needs is an animal friend.



Introducing, Mister Ginger!
State.Name: Mister Ginger (cat NPC)

State.Author: Bagi
State.Description: Adds a new custom NPC for East Scarp: Nora, an enthusiastic and talkative herpetologist, and her adorable pets, Stupid the gecko and Pinkie Pie the corn snake!
State.Name: Nora The Herpetologist - Custom NPC for East Scarp

State.Author: shekurika
State.Description: Allows to make the things needed for achieving Perfection easier.
State.Name: Perfection Tweaker

State.Author: Lemurkat
State.Description: After becoming the laughing stock of his peers for his 'outrageous' theories regarding the smoluanu, geologist Professor Jasper Thomas has returned to Pelican Town.  Can you help him overcome his embarrassment? Or will he fall prey to his obsession?
State.Name: Professor Jasper Thomas

State.Author: donutbunnybunny
State.Description: Seasonal Doghouses and Pet Bowls for Vanilla
State.Name: Seasonal Doghouses and Pet Bowls for Vanilla

State.Author: Himetarts and Wildflour
State.Description: Farmer's Market Furniture set for all of your fresh bread needs! 40+ pieces for Content Patcher.
State.Name: (CP) HxW Farmer's Market Furniture - Bakery Set

State.Author: LadyEleven
State.Description: A Content Patcher pack that layers snow on top of outdoor items in the winter.
State.Name: Snow-Covered Craftables

State.Author: focustense
State.Description: The definitive™ framework for building UI in Stardew Valley mods.
State.Name: StardewUI

State.Author: Urbanyeti
State.Description: Prevents failing milking/shearing attempts and adds an indicator when pets and animals can be petted, milked, or sheared.
State.Name: Better Ranching

State.Author: LavenderSkelly
State.Description: Replaces Dwarf's Portrait and Several other Dwarf NPC's Portraits as well.
State.Name: Dwarf Portrait Replacement

State.Author: Lemurkat
State.Description: Expands the characters of Marnie and Jas, with additional dialogue, new heart events, and an actual story arc!
State.Name: The Ranch Expansion Marnie and Jas

State.Author: DeLiXx
State.Description:
Unlockable Bundles enables content creators to add their own custom bundles into the game with ease.

Anything from a small repairable bridge to elaborate custom community centers is feasible.

Create farm upgrades, shortcuts, repairable structures, quest npcs or even your own ginger island expansion.
State.Name: Unlockable Bundles

State.Author: MoonSlime
State.Description: Gain EXP and unlock new recipes and professions through the cooking skill!
State.Name: YACS - Yet Another Cooking Skill

State.Author: Yagisan
State.Description: Enables purchasing of a selection of useful item from Clint's shop
State.Name: Yagisan's Clint Shop Expanded

State.Description: Adds blue eggs and blue mayo for blue chickens, as well as golden mayo from golden eggs.
State.Name: (CP) Blue Eggs and Golden Mayo

State.Author: AndrewJamesC
State.Description: Ever wonder how Lewis stays mayor all these years? Or why Pierre never visits his beautiful balcony? All that and more is answered in A Pelican Town, a small NPC expansion adding 2 new characters to the Valley! Meet Thompson and Kenzie, two colorful villagers made to explore some of the lesser thought-about parts of the game.
State.Name: A Pelican Town - NPC Expansion Mod

State.Author: Sandman53
State.Description: Abilities Experience Bars updated to 1.6 and added support for additional skill mods
State.Name: Abilities - Experience Bars 1.6

State.Author: PeacefulEnd
State.Description: Framework which enables texture variation for placeable objects, buildings and entities in Stardew Valley.
State.Name: Alternative Textures

State.Author: Pathoschild
State.Description: Place a chest next to a machine (like a furnace or crystalarium), and the machine will automatically pull raw items from the chest and push processed items into it. Connect multiple machines with a chest to link them.
State.Name: Automate

State.Author: maddogofblank
State.Description: Small expansion mod concerning the story of the Bear family and their life in the Valley, bringing new recipes, items, and romances. Story and Most Art by Mad Dog, House Exterior + Additional Building Assets by Yri, Music by TheFrenchDodo, advice, inspiration, and encouragement from the East Scarp discord.
State.Name: Bear Family Custom NPCS - An Add-On for East Scarp

State.Author: Khloe Leclair
State.Description: A new crafting UI with support for customizable categories and favorites. Easy bulk crafting. Better Workbench functionality. And, optionally, constructing buildings right from the crafting menu using an extra mod.
State.Name: Better Crafting

State.Author: aedenthorn
State.Description: Lets you tweak lightning rod and lightning strike settings.
State.Name: Better Lightning Rods

State.Author: Pathoschild
State.Description: Access your chests, dressers, fridge, shipping bin, and Junimo huts from anywhere and organise them your way. Transfer items without having to run around, from the comfort of your bed to the deepest mine level. Includes optional balanced mode.
State.Name: Chests Anywhere

State.Author: Agent Lyoko
State.Description: Rewrites Clint's dialogue to be less weird toward both the player and Emily and making him slightly more well-adjusted.
State.Name: Clint Rewritten

State.Author: AndrewJC
State.Description: A small expansion adding 4 new NPCs, new locations, new fish and more. Meet the farmers of Coal Point Farm!
State.Name: Coal Point Farm - Custom NPCs

State.Author: LemurKat
State.Description: Finished the Community Center and sad that it now lies almost empty? Now it really will serve a purpose as heart of the community.
State.Name: Community Center Reimagined

Original.Name: Community Park Decor for Content Patcher-31367-1-1-2-1739930130.zip

State.Author: FarmerBeans
State.Description: Adds Vanilla-style Park furniture and decor with its own catalog you can buy from Robin's shop. Design Community park spaces, farmer's markets and more.  Requires Content Patcher and Calcifer.
State.Name: Community Park Decorations for Content Patcher

State.Author: Cornucopia
State.Description: Adds more artisan machines and goods to the game. Fully configurable and written to rely primarily on Content Patcher.
State.Name: Cornucopia - Artisan Machines

State.Author: Cornucopia
State.Description: Adds more flowers , flower bushes, and flower trees to the game. Fully configurable and written to rely primarily on Content Patcher.
State.Name: Cornucopia - More Flowers

State.Author: TheFrenchDodo
State.Description:
Meet two-time award winner, author Rodney O'Brien! 

This mod adds a new NPC to East Scarp. A friendly writer who happens to be Elliott's uncle.
State.Name: Creative Differences - NPC Rodney (East Scarp)

State.Author: Digus
State.Description: Adds a way to customize the casks. It comes configurable with Pickles and Maple Syrup but can be changed to add any 'Object' and change the time of the products that already work on casks. You can also enable casks to work outside the cellar.
State.Name: Custom Cask Mod

State.Author: Pathoschild
State.Description: Overlay the world with visual data like bee/Junimo/scarecrow/sprinkler coverage, hidden paths and warps, and more.
State.Name: Data Layers

State.Author: Agent Lyoko - original mod by LiveOnSUPERT
State.Description: Go on dates after marriage with your spouse(s)! An updated version of Date Night that works on 1.6. Requires Stardew Valley 1.6.4+.
State.Name: Date Night Redux

State.Author: MouseyPounds
State.Description: Dish of the Day Display is a SMAPI mod which adds a localized chat message and/or an in-game sign indicating what special food item Gus is selling at the Saloon each day.
State.Name: Dish of the Day Display

State.Author: Tenebrous Nova
State.Description: Eli & Dylan is an add-on to East Scarp featuring a cryptologist/marine biologist brother duo that includes new items, locations, crops, fish, and more!
State.Name: Eli and Dylan - Custom NPCs for East Scarp

State.Author: Elle
State.Description: Adds seasonal overlays to vanilla farm buildings
State.Name: Elle's Seasonal Vanilla Buildings

State.Author: shekurika
State.Description: This mod adds a GUI and two commands that allow to lookup events by ID/character name. It also has a function to show all events that are available to you today in an ingame interface.
State.Name: Event Lookup

State.Author: Selph aka zombifier
State.Description: Adds extra features to Content Patcher-added machine artisan recipes, such as defining extra fuels or byproducts for specific recipes.
State.Name: Extra Machine Configs

State.Author: Paul Steele
State.Description: Tired of selling millions of blueberries every summer? Want to try out various crop mods but can't resist the urge to min max? Ferngill Simple Economy introduces a randomized economy where crops follow basic rules of supply and demand. Sell too much of an item and its price may plummet! But play the market right and you might strike it big.
State.Name: Ferngill Simple Economy

State.Author: cajcbell
State.Description: Adds a seasonal boat to the docks with new NPCs and a random item exchange system.
State.Name: FIASA - a mini expansion

State.Author: Agent Lyoko
State.Description: Adds unique acceptance responses to vanilla datable characters at the Flower Dance! Requires Custom Fixed Dialogue.
State.Name: Flower Dance Acceptance Responses

State.Author: Selph aka zombifier
State.Description: Be rewarded for selling fresh, high quality produce. Increase sell price of high quality crops and other organic items, and add a season-long competition to crown the farm with the highest variety of fresh produce in all of the Ferngill Republic!
State.Name: Fresh Farm Produce

State.Author: spacechase0
State.Description: Adds an in-game UI to edit other mods' config options.
State.Name: Generic Mod Config Menu

State.Author: Cornucopia
State.Description: A configurable mod that adds a few new crops to grow vanilla forage items, as well as converts some vanilla crops into perennial "bushes".
State.Name: Growable Forage and Crop Bushes

State.Author: bungus
State.Description: Shows how event dialogue options will impact friendship. Highly customizable!
State.Name: Heart Event Helper

State.Author: Pathoschild
State.Description: Summon your horse anywhere (even in the deepest mines) at the press of a button or by using the horse flute.
State.Name: Horse Flute Anywhere

State.Author: Goldenrevolver
State.Description:
Make the horse the way it should be, thin, fast and useful. Put items into its saddle bags, pet it and give it water and food to befriend your horse to increase its movement speed. 



Also includes a menu to check on horse or pet friendship and adds sound effects to the previously silent horse.
State.Name: Horse Overhaul - Thin - Faster - Saddle Bags - Friendship

State.Author: Himetarts and Wildflour
State.Description:
Hey kid. 

You wanna build your own bakery?

Boy do I got 50+ furniture items for you.
State.Name: (CP) Hxw Bakery and Cafe Furniture

State.Author: HimeTarts and Wildflourmods
State.Description: 80+ adorable potted plants and hanging planters as new furniture pieces for you to decorate your farmhouse, shed, or anywhere needs plants! (Everywhere needs more plants). Built in foliage recolor support and seven different flower overlay choices.
State.Name: HxW Decorative Plants Furniture Set

State.Author: Himetarts and Wildflour
State.Description: Whimsical outdoor furniture set for AT & D
State.Name: (DGA AT) HxW Fairy Garden Furniture

State.Description: Whimsical indoor furniture set for Content Patcher ! For when you wish to turn your home into a fairy's paradise.
State.Name: HxW Fairy Garden Furniture Indoors

State.Author: Himetarts and Wildflour
State.Description: Farmer's Market Furniture set for all of your farmer and merchant needs! 100+ pieces for Content Patcher
State.Name: (CP) HxW Farmer's Market Furniture - Core

State.Author: Himetarts and Wildflour
State.Description: Stylish outdoor furniture set for DGA or AT.
State.Name: (DGA AT) HxW Outdoor Furniture

State.Author: Himetarts and Wildflour
State.Description: Adds 75+ new plant filled furniture pieces for that eco-loving heart of yours.

State.Name: (CP) HxW Romantic Furniture

State.Author: beyondrecovery
State.Description: Makes Sandy more immersive by giving her a more dynamic schedule, more events, and more dialogue, with optional Sandy/Emily rival hearts events!
State.Name: Immersive Sandy

State.Author: Jibblestein
State.Description:
A content pack for MinecartPatcher that adds new minecarts to certain locations for convenience and also integrates minecarts from Ridgeside Village and East Scarp into the vanilla minecart network. Placement of new minecarts also has SVE in mind.



Includes translations for Chinese, Russian, and Portuguese
State.Name: Integrated Minecarts

State.Author: Malic
State.Description:
Jade is a self-proclaimed entomologist, lover of all things magical, and generally an odd person to meet.

Fully romanceable and marryable. Can you figure out this odd girls secrets?
State.Name: Jade NPC

State.Author: LemurKat
State.Description:
Juliet is a troubled young woman exiled to Pelican Town for reasons unknown, but possibly linked to her sharp-tongue and flirty, irrepressible nature. Her

co-worker, housemate, and friend, Jessie is matronly, empathic, and a keen gardener and herbalist.
State.Name: Juliet and Jessie the Joja Clerks

State.Author: Pathoschild
State.Description: See live info about whatever's under your cursor when you press F1. Learn a villager's favourite gifts, when a crop will be ready to harvest, how long a fence will last, why your farm animals are unhappy, and more.
State.Name: Lookup Anything

State.Author: MoonSlime
State.Description: Spacecore luck is a port of the luck skill to use the Spacecore API instead of trying to enable the hidden vanilla luck skill. It also introduces a few tweaks that are to my taste.
State.Name: Spacecore Luck Skill

State.Author: Lumisteria
State.Description: This mod is a resource mod for map modder adding a new tilesheet containing various buildings to use in their map. Pls read the instructions to know how the mod works !
State.Name: Lumisteria Tilesheets - Outdoor

State.Author: Digus
State.Description: Framework to use the in game mailbox. Console commands to adjust the mail. Code and Content Pack interfaces.
State.Name: Mail Framework Mod

State.Author: Squeaks
State.Description: An add-on to East Scarp that Introduces a friendly beekeeper with more than a few secrets.
State.Name: Metalcore Goes Cottagecore - East Scarp Addon

State.Author: MissCoriel
State.Description: Tired of everyone responding with "...!! I'll accept this. Thank you." When you give them flowers?  Want them to accept your pendant in a way more to their character?  Want your custom NPCs to as well.. Then look no further!!
State.Name: MissCoriel's NPC Unique Courtship Response 5 - Gifting Friends

State.Author: Pathoschild
State.Description: Enable noclip at the press of a button, letting you walk through anything (even map boundaries).
State.Name: Noclip Mode

State.Description: See NPC and players on the map, with an optional minimap.

State.Name: Remapping - Minimap Project

State.Author: Rafseazz and mamaesh - Assisted by RSV Council
State.Description: Ridgeside Village adds over 50 new NPCs, a new location, new items, new shops, new festivals, custom music, custom quests, and more!
State.Name: Ridgeside Village

State.Author: Kailey
State.Description: Replaces the standard wedding arch with a seasonal wooden one.
State.Name: Seasonal Wedding Arch

State.Author: aedenthorn and FlyingTNT
State.Description: Shows information in shops on whether seeds can be planted today (with or without fertilizer) and the value of their various produce items.

State.Description: Skip the intro logos, and optionally skip straight to the load or co-op screen.

State.Description: Adds a skill and professions related to talking with and helping townspeople.

State.Description: A framework mod used by some of my other mods.
State.Name: SpaceCore

State.Author: DestyNova
State.Description: Introducing the "swords" half of "swords and sorcery" to East Scarp! Befriend our resident rogue, Mateo, as they embark on their thrilling expedition into an all new era of adventures.
State.Name: Never Ending Adventure - NPC Mateo

Original.Name: The Last Smoluanu A Dwarf Expansion-9642-1-1-4-1740383748.zip

State.Author: LemurKat
State.Description: Expanding on the character and lore of Dwarf, the lonely demihuman keeping shop in Pelican Town's mine. Adds dialogue, events, and a special roommate "proposal" item so this mischievous little gremlin can come live with you.
State.Name: The Last Smoluanu - A Dwarf Expansion.

State.Author: Shaklin
State.Description:
With this mod all players in multiplayer, depending on their spouse, have different looking children.

Of course, you can also use it in single player.
State.Name: Unique Children

State.Author: PrincessFelicie
State.Description: Adds 150+ lines of dialogue related to gifting townies specific items.
State.Name: Unique Gift Dialogues Expanded

State.Author: Cherry
State.Description: Upgrade uninhabited cabins and remove their seed boxes and beds
State.Name: Upgrade Empty Cabins

State.Author: Andrew Young
State.Description: Right-click with your watering can and watch yourself water your crops! Unlike other mods, the crops won't be instantly watered. Your farmer will go crop by crop watering them, expending the same amount of time and energy as if you had done it yourself to keep as vanilla as possible, but a lot less tedious!
State.Name: Water Bot

Original.Name: Yagisan - Custom NPCs for NPC Map Locations-8174-1-2-1-1716720023.7z

State.Author: Yagisan
State.Description: This mod was created to show custom NPC's on the world map using NPC Map Locations. It does not include any maps.
State.Name: Yagisan's Custom NPCs for NPC Map Locations

State.Author: NanoIsNotRobot
State.Description: A set of retro style furniture, using the AT mode
State.Name: (AT) Nano's Retro Style Furniture

State.Author: TheLimeyDragon
State.Description: Ayeisha is a custom NPC who works for the Ferngill Postal Service. Who has a number of delivery events of vanilla and some custom characters.
State.Name: Ayeisha - The Postal Worker (Custom NPC)

State.Author: DaisyNiko
State.Description: just the tilesheets
State.Name: DaisyNiko's Tilesheets

State.Author: Aimon111
State.Description: A small expansion mod for Stardew Valley. This mod changes the look of vanilla Witch Swamp map, making it look more lively and realistic. Adds new endgame NPC, quests, items, fish, crops, forage and more!
State.Name: Distant Lands -  A Small Witch Swamp Expansion

State.Description: Fievel the Hat Mouse finds a home in East Scarp! Can you help him learn not to be afraid of cats? Join him and other ES critters on a wholesome, hat-tastic adventure!
State.Name: Fievel Goes East Scarp - Hat Mouse NPC

State.Author: kelly2892
State.Description: A mod that makes the player not only wear proper attire to the Flower Dance, but also dance the same as the NPCs.
State.Name: Flower Dancing - A Flower Dance Mod

State.Author: Himetarts and Wildflour
State.Description: A resource for modders including (most) of the H&W furniture suite to be used for your maps!

State.Author: Elle and Asterisk555
State.Description: Alternative Textures packs for Elle's Seasonal Buildings! Includes options to match several map recolors.

Original.Name: Lurking in the Dark - Luau Dialogue Fix-10770-3-0-8-1745814898.zip

State.Description: Adds a new shadow guy NPC to East Scarp!
State.Name: Lurking in the Dark - NPC Sen (East Scarp)

State.Author: SiTheGreat1
State.Description: Help Morris redeem himself after completing the Community Center! Features 11 events and multiple schedules.
State.Name: Morris Redeemed

State.Description: Help save the Saloon and open Stardrop Breakfast for business! An series of events, special orders, and immersive schedules revolving around the Saloon.

State.Author: CC
State.Description: Add a Forest Ranger to Cindersap Forest, and explore a story about morals versus mission.

State.Author: Tikamin557
State.Description:
The obelisk will be miniaturized to improve visibility.

Floors can also be changed in detail.

There is also the appearance of the season.

RSV, ES, DTZ, DWM, SWO (Custom Obelisks), can also be set.
State.Name: Mini Obelisk (Alternative Textures version)

State.Description: Various fixes/QOL improvements for Farmhouse/Cabins, intended for mod creators and mod users alike.

State.Author: Shockah
State.Description: Ever hated having to put a sprinkler in the middle of your crops? Ever wanted to make a layout that isn't 5x5? Now you can!

State.Description: The mod loader for Stardew Valley.

State.Author: EideeHi
State.Description: Customizable Mod for easy fishing.

State.Author: Speshkitty
State.Description: Adjusts the outputs for seed makers based on the inputs

State.Author: mistyspring
State.Description: Adds a spouse patio for Krobus when he's the farmer's roommate.
State.Name: Spouse patio for Krobus - seasonal

State.Name: Destroyable Bushes

State.Author: PeacefulEnd
State.Description: Greenhouse Gatherers is a mod for Stardew Valley that adds a way for Junimos to harvest crops inside buildings.

State.Description: This is a technical mod to help diagnose and triage performance problems in other mods.
State.Name: Profiler

State.Author: mushymato
State.Description: Framework for custom trinkets and companions.
